reviewText: It's ok, but I was hoping for something more in depth.
I am a French teacher and I bought this to share with students. I love documentaries, however, I could not even get through this one.
Got this before heading off to France last spring and it was a delightful preview of some of the locales we were about to visit! So we knew where to look not to miss some great sites!
What a great video..it really shows France up close and personal.  If you travel the world while sitting in your arm chair..this video is for you... do not miss seeing it.
